    "Html": "I would like to have a dialog box displayed when a command is executed, and have the dialog box centered in the main window of the application.<br>\r\nThe execute command is defined in a module, so I'm unsure how to set the owner property of the dialog box.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAny ideas?<br>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2008-12-15T22:36:03.533-08:00",
